description:
Enjoy the video of Nina Zakharenko in which she invites the entire community to participate in Pycon Colombia 2022.

Social Networks:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/nnja
Github: https://github.com/nnja
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/nnja/

Pycon Colombia 2022 in this edition brings great guests and this year we will have the participation of Nina Zakharenko a software engineer with over a decade of experience. She's currently the Principal Lead of the Python Developer Advocacy team at Microsoft.

This is the beginning of great announcements, follow us on our social networks so you don't miss any updates.
